## R Markdown

```{r readRDS provided<-TRUE}
precip <- readRDS("USAAnnualPcpn1950_2008.rds")
temp <- readRDS("USAAnnualTemp1950_2008.rds")
```
```{r Remove NA values}
precip_wo_na <- precip[complete.cases(precip), ]
temp_wo_na <- temp[complete.cases(temp), ]
```

```{r Aggregation}
year = precip_wo_na$year
name = precip_wo_na$name
lat = precip_wo_na$lat
lon = precip_wo_na$lon
precip_agg <- aggregate(year ~ lat+lon+name, data = precip_wo_na, FUN=length)
```
